<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَتَعْمِيمُهُ بِالْمَا اشْتَرِطْ وَبِخَرَقَةٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِيُمْنَ وَسَمِّ وَانْوِ شَرْطًا بِأَجْوَدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلا تُدْخِلَنَّ الْمَاءَ فَاهُ وَأَنْفَهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَنَظِّفْهُمَا وَاتْمِمْ وُضُوءَ التَّعَبُّدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمِنْ رُغْوَةِ السِّدْرِ اغْسِلَنْهُ جَمِيعَهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَبِالأَيْمَنِ ابْدَأْ ثُمَّ لِلأَيْسَرِ أُقْصدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ثَلاثًا فَإِنَّ لَمْ يُنْقِ أَوْ بَانَ جَمِيعِهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَغَسِّلْ إِلَى الأَنْقَى وَبِالْوِتْرِ جَدِّدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِلَى مُنْتَهَى سَبْعٍ وَفِي كُلِّ غَسْلَةٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَقَلِّبْهُ وَأرْفِقْ وَامْسَحْ الْبَطْنَ بِالْيَدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَفِي الآخِرِ الْكَافُورَ ضَعْهُ فَإِنْ بَدَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِذَا بَعْدَ سَبْعٍ مَخْرَجَ الْمَيِّتِ فَأسْدُدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>بِقُطْنٍ فَإِنْ يَخْرُجِ فَطِينٍ وَقِيلَ لا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تُغَسِّلْ وَوَضِّ بَعْدَ غُسْلِ الأَذَى قَدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ تَسْرِيحُ الشُّعُورِ بَأَوْطَدٍ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَشَارِبَهُ وَالظِّفْرُ وَالإِبْطَ فَأجْدُدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَغَسِّلْ وَكَفِّنْ بَعْضَ مَيِّتٍ مُغَيَّبٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَصَلِّ عَلَيْهِ مِثْلَ رِجْلٍ بِأَوْكَدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَيُخْتَارُ لِلْغُسْلِ الأَمِينُ وَعَالِمٌ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>بِأَحْكَامِ تَغْسِيلٍ وَلَوْ بِتَقَلُّدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَلا تُفْشِ سِرًّا يُؤَثِّرُ الْمَيْتُ كَتْمَهُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>سِوَى ذِي فُجُورٍ وَابْتَدَاعٍ مُعَوَّدِ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>